name: Ashley Resident Evil 4 Lora
description:
Had a go at making my own Ashley Lora! Let me know what you think?

My standard for this prompt is as follows:

<lora:ashley:0.4>, ashley, short blonde hair, ((orange sweater)), red scarf, ((green tartan skirt))

I was actually quite happy with this, released it on my patreon, but thought I'd release it her as well.

More examples using this Lora are on my Pixiv.

If you've got more idea, please let me know!

Want me to make a LORA for you: https://www.fiverr.com/s2/c47476ec9d

If you want to support me, find my patreon and Fanbox at: https://www.patreon.com/LMJA18 and https://lmja18.fanbox.cc/ or see more of my images over at https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/52924269
